law.text:
The commissioner shall, through the promulgation of administrative regulations:
Establish the procedures necessary to implement KRS 198B. 6401 to 198B.6417;
Establish an inactive status of certification for fire sprinkler inspectors who are not actively conducting inspections but wish to maintain their certification;
Establish a waiver of insurance requirements for inactive certifications;
Establish the reactivation procedure for a certification successfully placed into inactive status; and
Establish criteria for approval of continuing education providers and continuing education courses.
